node.text:
EXCITING NEWS! We’re partnering up with @thepeopleconcern for #GivingTuesday to help fund their efforts to end homelessness. The People Concern is one of LA’s largest housing + social service agencies and we’re so excited to announce that 5% of today’s sales will be donated directly to them. 

PS! The cyber sale has been extended so you can enjoy the discount while shopping for a good cause 🤍
